OL,5,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe competition kicks off at The
OL,7,     FRed Lion in Charing Heath, Kent,
OL,8,     Fwhere the B&Bers are treated to a
OL,9,     Fmasterclass in hospitality. And
OL,10,     Fone guest reveals their combative
OL,11,     Fside.
OL,12,G1855 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIn East Sussex, Dean and Becky
OL,14,     Fhope their unique glamping digs,
OL,15,     FGlamp in Style - including a
OL,16,     Fconverted army truck and a
OL,17,     Fhorsebox - will have the B&Bers
OL,18,     Fraving. If only...
