OL,5,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FPayment day promises to be a fiery
OL,7,     Faffair, with two sets of B&Bers
OL,8,     Fset for a head-on collision about
OL,9,     Ftheir marking. And then we find
OL,10,     Fout who's won.
OL,11,G2100 The Emergency Ward
OL,12,     FAt The Royal Melbourne Hospital's
OL,13,     Fmajor trauma centre, Dr Taylor's
OL,14,     Fpatient deteriorates with a
OL,15,     Fsuspected brain bleed. Dr Tristan
OL,16,     FHarding straightens a young man's
OL,17,     Fdislocated ankle.
